headline: Piper Sandler Maintains Overweight on Willis Towers Watson, Lowers Price Target to $341
summary: Piper Sandler  analyst Paul Newsome   maintains Willis Towers Watson (NASDAQ:WTW) with a Overweight and lowers the price target from $365 to $341.
